title: Mental Abuse- Come on Baby- NY Hardcore flac Rare
description:
Mental Abuse- Come on Baby- NY Hardcore flac Rare 

This is a very rare recording of Mental Abuse this was recorded in 1985 on Blue Vinyl and the only digital copy available. Ipurchased this 12 inch record titled Message from America on Urinal Records December 12 1985 outside of CBGB&#039;s for 5 bucks. This record does include tracks from the Agnostic Front original 7 inch. I will be ripping this record complete as soon as I get familiar with the software and can bring you the best possible digital copy.
